name: Helpthemove
tag_list: real-estate, estate-agents, online-service, energy, broadband, internet, television
description: Services for estate agents and tenants.
overview:
Is a services management platform for estate agents and their tenants.

Working across three major industries with over 15 blue chip partners.

Offering great deals to tenants in the form of discounted products and unique incentives. Helping tenants to get the best deals in the market.

They offer their services through their estate agent members who generate an income for each sale they help to generate.

Services are completely free for the estate agents and require a short authorisation process when joining to become certified.
